title: Bill Stax (Vasco) parties it up in '38 Flexing' MV | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Bill Stax (Vasco) parties it up in '38 Flexing' MV By KpopJoA 36 minutes ago 1,365 111 1 0 Google+ Rapper Vasco has released his first single under the name Bill Stax titled "38 Flexing." 
Featuring a black and white color grade, the video shows the singer partying it up in the club to looking out the window of a high-rise in solitude. Like its namesake, the song talks about flexing or flaunting and how he's one of the top rappers in Korea (38 in the song title comes from Vasco's age). 
The track was produced #jaykidman and the MV was directed by Woody Answer Jr . This is the title track for Bill Stax's first mixtape which will be released on March 3.
